7.text: Mother: Let’s get ready to go to the airport to pick them up.

8.text: Lahiru: Mother, remember, we needn’t go to the airport. They’ll take a taxi to come here.

9.text: Mother: Ah yes, you told me about it this morning.

10.text: Father: Are you sure of it?

11.text: Lahiru: Yes, father. I checked with him when he wrote to me last.

12.text: Mother: All right. Lahiru, you have to help me to prepare dinner.
